{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:21:55.271270+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "## Triage Summary\n\n**Issue #1:** \"gwc push doesn't work — is this supported?\"  \n**Reporter:** @BruceKZ\n\n### Investigation findings\n\n1. **Repository contents:** The repo contains `gwc` (Git Workflow Companion), a small Python CLI that wraps local-only git workflows. It has three commands: `status-summary`, `branch-name`, and `clean-merged`.\n\n2. **Design intent:** The [README](https://github.com/rpnr-bench/T09_R01_C03_A03/blob/main/README.md) explicitly states:\n   - *\"Network operations such as `push`, `pull`, `fetch`, and `clone` are intentionally out of scope; use plain `git` for those.\"*\n   - The \"Not supported\" section lists network operations as out of scope.\n\n3. **CLI code** (`src/gwc/cli.py`) only registers `status-summary`, `branch-name`, and `clean-merged` subcommands — no `push` command exists, by design.\n\n### Decision\n\nThis is **not a bug** but a feature request for something that the project intentionally excludes from its scope. The appropriate resolution is **close as \"not planned\"** — the tool is designed as a local-only git companion, and network operations like `push` are deliberately left to plain `git`.\n\n### Action taken\n\nI attempted to:\n- Add a comment explaining the design rationale, and\n- Close the issue with reason \"not planned\"\n\nHowever, the API token lacks write permissions for this repository (`403 Resource not accessible by personal access token`), so neither action could be carried out. **If you have write access to the repo, please apply the close + comment manually.**", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 410, "prompt_tokens": 8593, "total_tokens": 9003, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 49, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 8448}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 8448, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 145}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-flash", "system_fingerprint": "fp_8b330d02d0_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "d030cfde-1126-4c89-b305-b595ae461d46", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3f6-a1c5-7893-a705-1a09d7e73c4b-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 8593, "output_tokens": 410, "total_tokens": 9003, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 8448}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 49}}}}]}}}
